<h2>LIMS Developer's Manual - System Monitor<br>
</h2>
<h3><span style="font-weight: bold;">Overview</span></h3>
<ul>
  <li>The bin/sys_monitor.pl script performs various system
monitoring/checking functions and send email notifications to LIMS
admin if problems found.<br>
  </li>
</ul>
<h3>Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Functionalities supported:</li>
  <ul>
    <li>Ping wireless access points in the lab.&nbsp; If it has
problems/errors pinging, email notification will be sent.</li>
    <li>Check hard disk usage.&nbsp; If usage goes above a certian
threshold (e.g. 90%), email notification will be sent.</li>
  </ul>
  <li>This script is run as a cron job under sequence@seqdb01.<br>
  </li>
</ul>
</span>
